    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape, runs super smoothly, and has been really well-taken care of over the years. Perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend road trips! I\u2019m looking for a quick, easy sale to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
